divs: Sighting DetailsI work nights at Dell Childrens Hospital and I was peering out of my patients window when I saw this strange object floating in the air. It was about the size of an airplane, but definitely not an airplane. It was glowing green. It was strange because it almost seemed to know I spotted it because when I went to get my phone to take a picture it was gone.
Summary: I saw a small strange aircraft hovering over my place of work
